<body>
<div xml:space="preserve">
<p begin="8300000t" end="25000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle0">那么安兹大人</p>
<p begin="25000000t" end="70000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle1">我会让里．耶斯提杰王国<br />见识一下魔导国的存在</p>
<p begin="81300000t" end="100500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle2">光看这个使节团</p>
<p begin="100400000t" end="134200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle3">就能让王国的人民<br />了解到魔导国的实力</p>
<p begin="141700000t" end="163400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle4">不过你要留心一点</p>
<p begin="163290000t" end="203700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle5">因为现在还没看到<br />洗脑夏提雅的那些人</p>
<p begin="203800000t" end="213000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle6">是</p>
<p begin="212900000t" end="252900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle7">绝对不能放开这个真实之无<br />我会谨记在心</p>
<p begin="252900000t" end="308300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle8">只要有了那个<br />就不会被世界级道具洗脑</p>
<p begin="308300000t" end="343300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle9">这是你第一次到外面去</p>
<p begin="343300000t" end="379600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle10">如果觉得有危险就立刻撤退</p>
<p begin="379600000t" end="400000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle11">你有携带转移类的道具吗</p>
<p begin="400000000t" end="436300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle12">有些敌人也会妨碍转移进行攻击</p>
<p begin="436300000t" end="459600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle13">你有想好要怎么对付这些人吗</p>
<p begin="459600000t" end="471300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle14">还有…</p>
<p begin="480800000t" end="498700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle15">就到此为止吧</p>
<p begin="498800000t" end="521300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle16">然后迪米乌哥斯他…</p>
<p begin="521300000t" end="540900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle17">算了 没什么</p>
<p begin="540800000t" end="560400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle18">真的没事吗</p>
<p begin="569600000t" end="593800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle19">虽然很想知道迪米乌哥斯在想什么</p>
<p begin="593800000t" end="645500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle20">但是身为至高无上统治者的我<br />也没办法叫他告诉我</p>
<p begin="645400000t" end="665000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle21">最后我再提醒你一件事</p>
<p begin="665000000t" end="694200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle22">季节交替的时候很容易引发感冒</p>
<p begin="694200000t" end="718800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle23">就算拥有能完全抵御疾病的抗性</p>
<p begin="718800000t" end="753000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle24">这个世界也有可能<br />还有抗性无法抵御的疾病</p>
<p begin="752900000t" end="767500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle25">你要注意健康哦</p>
<p begin="767500000t" end="778300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle26">安兹大人</p>
<p begin="778300000t" end="812500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle27">我知道一种非常有效的预防药</p>
<p begin="812500000t" end="823300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle28">这样啊</p>
<p begin="823300000t" end="838300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle29">就是接吻</p>
<p begin="838300000t" end="848300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle30">接吻</p>
<p begin="848300000t" end="905400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle31">只要接吻就能缓解压力<br />使副交感神经变活跃 提高免疫力</p>
<p begin="905400000t" end="931700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle32">也就是说只要接吻就不会生病</p>
<p begin="931700000t" end="953000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle33">所以请您吻我</p>
<p begin="1064200000t" end="1097100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle34">嘴对嘴接吻感觉有点太夸张了</p>
<p begin="1097100000t" end="1112100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle35">所以我吻了你的脸颊</p>
<p begin="1112100000t" end="1147100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle36">我还以为您绝对不会理我</p>
<p begin="1206700000t" end="1230500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle37">雅儿贝德 你别哭了</p>
<p begin="1302890000t" end="1329200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle38">雅儿贝德 别哭了</p>
<p begin="1372500000t" end="1385800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle39">没事了吗</p>
<p begin="1385800000t" end="1404600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle40">是 安兹大人</p>
<p begin="1404600000t" end="1442500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle41">让您看到我如此丢脸的一面<br />真的非常抱歉</p>
<p begin="1442500000t" end="1470400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle42">是吗 那你可以走了</p>
<p begin="1470400000t" end="1504600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle43">遵命 莫莫伽大人</p>
<p begin="1567900000t" end="1591700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle44">忘了刚刚在这里发生的事</p>
<p begin="1591700000t" end="1609600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle45">遵命</p>
<p begin="1624600000t" end="1671700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle46">(斯连教国最深处)<br />今天也感谢神赐予我们人类</p>
<p begin="1671700000t" end="1691300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle47">得以活下去的生命</p>
<p begin="1691300000t" end="1716700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle48">谢谢您</p>
<p begin="1742500000t" end="1787500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle49">第一个议题<br />是关于安兹．乌尔．恭魔导国</p>
<p begin="1787500000t" end="1824600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle50">(土之神官长)<br />之前在卡兹平原与帝国的战斗</p>
<p begin="1824600000t" end="1854200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle51">(雷蒙．札古．罗兰桑)<br />安兹．乌尔．恭</p>
<p begin="1854200000t" end="1884600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle52">对里．耶斯提杰王国军<br />造成毁灭性的伤害</p>
<p begin="1884600000t" end="1915900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle53">恭夺走王国的都市重镇耶．兰提尔</p>
<p begin="1915800000t" end="1948700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle54">宣布建立安兹．乌尔．恭魔导国</p>
<p begin="1948800000t" end="2000100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle55">帝国皇帝艾尔．尼克斯颁布圣旨<br />要求周边的各国承认这件事</p>
<p begin="2000000000t" end="2022100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle56">(风之神官长)<br />不死者统治的国家啊</p>
<p begin="2022100000t" end="2039200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle57">(多米尼克．伊雷．珀鲁托修)<br />那岂不是地狱吗</p>
<p begin="2039200000t" end="2056300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle58">(光之神官长)<br />果然不应该默认</p>
<p begin="2056300000t" end="2078400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle59">(伊万．贾斯纳．多拉库罗)<br />而是应该阻止这件事吧</p>
<p begin="2078300000t" end="2109200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle60">(火之神官长)<br />与恭作对是一件危险的事</p>
<p begin="2109200000t" end="2130500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle61">(贝妮丝．娜古雅．桑提妮)<br />不是已经有共识了吗</p>
<p begin="2130400000t" end="2152900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle62">(暗之神官长)<br />帝国到底在想什么</p>
<p begin="2152900000t" end="2182900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle63">(马克西米利安．欧雷．拉奇耶)<br />难不成是被他用魔法操控了吗</p>
<p begin="2182900000t" end="2197500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle64">(水之神官长)<br />那是不可能的</p>
<p begin="2197500000t" end="2222100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle65">(席内丁．德兰．桂尔夫)<br />那里有帕拉戴恩在</p>
<p begin="2227500000t" end="2280000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle66">这次的战争有漆黑圣典<br />占星千里监视</p>
<p begin="2280000000t" end="2312500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle67">但是因为诸多问题<br />所以报告的有点晚</p>
<p begin="2312500000t" end="2331700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle68">还请各位见谅</p>
<p begin="2331700000t" end="2358000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle69">各位手上的报告书上写的</p>
<p begin="2357900000t" end="2391200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle70">是占星千里亲口所说的话</p>
<p begin="2408300000t" end="2435400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle71">雷蒙 这是真的吗</p>
<p begin="2435400000t" end="2487900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle72">如果各位相信占星千里说的话<br />就是真的</p>
<p begin="2487900000t" end="2533700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle73">在场根本没有人不相信她说的话</p>
<p begin="2533800000t" end="2545100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle74">但是…</p>
<p begin="2545000000t" end="2560400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle75">死亡骑士</p>
<p begin="2560400000t" end="2587900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle76">预估难度超过100的不死者</p>
<p begin="2587900000t" end="2605400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle77">居然约有500名</p>
<p begin="2605400000t" end="2625000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle78">难道不是幻术吗</p>
<p begin="2625000000t" end="2659200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle79">占星千里不可能会看错</p>
<p begin="2659200000t" end="2709600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle80">我们也在魔导国的首都<br />发现多名死亡骑士</p>
<p begin="2709600000t" end="2757900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle81">那么负责守护人们的我们<br />能采取的最佳手段是什么呢</p>
<p begin="2757900000t" end="2803700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle82">这就要看漆黑圣典能不能做出处置</p>
<p begin="2803800000t" end="2817100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle83">不可能的</p>
<p begin="2817100000t" end="2858800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle84">我以前任漆黑圣典<br />第三席的身份告诉各位</p>
<p begin="2858800000t" end="2901300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle85">想和数百名死亡骑士交手<br />根本就是痴人说梦</p>
<p begin="2901300000t" end="2949600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle86">不过神人就不一定了</p>
<p begin="2973800000t" end="3005500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle87">如果是继承神之血的那两个人</p>
<p begin="3005400000t" end="3057900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle88">就算死亡骑士大军攻过来<br />应该也能轻松应付</p>
<p begin="3057900000t" end="3080000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle89">那就放心了</p>
<p begin="3102100000t" end="3135900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle90">雷蒙 你在隐瞒什么</p>
<p begin="3135800000t" end="3173700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle91">席内丁长老 你是指什么</p>
<p begin="3173800000t" end="3195900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle92">我有一个问题</p>
<p begin="3195800000t" end="3236200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle93">为什么占星千里要把自己关起来</p>
<p begin="3236300000t" end="3269600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle94">是因为害怕不死者大军吗</p>
<p begin="3269600000t" end="3301700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle95">不是的 她是看见了绝望</p>
<p begin="3301700000t" end="3344200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle96">看见了只有神人才能战胜的力量<br />才会那样</p>
<p begin="3344200000t" end="3387500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle97">这份报告书应该不只这些吧</p>
<p begin="3387500000t" end="3425800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle98">我本来想先去寻找可能性</p>
<p begin="3425800000t" end="3457100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle99">这是占星千里所见的全部</p>
<p begin="3505000000t" end="3520400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle100">原来如此</p>
<p begin="3530800000t" end="3577500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle101">一开始看到这个确实会产生怀疑</p>
<p begin="3577500000t" end="3608300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle102">但是还是令人难以置信</p>
<p begin="3608300000t" end="3652900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle103">居然因为一个魔法<br />造成超过13万人死亡</p>
<p begin="3652900000t" end="3699600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle104">这是神的魔法 第11阶级魔法吧</p>
<p begin="3699600000t" end="3715400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle105">如果真是这样…</p>
<p begin="3715400000t" end="3735800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle106">神降临了啊</p>
<p begin="3735800000t" end="3756200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle107">终于降临了吗</p>
<p begin="3756300000t" end="3784600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle108">应该是 时隔200年了吧</p>
<p begin="3784600000t" end="3816300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle109">前提是传闻必须是真的</p>
<p begin="3816300000t" end="3859200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle110">可是王国提升国力的速度非常慢</p>
<p begin="3859200000t" end="3881300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle111">那群笨蛋</p>
<p begin="3881300000t" end="3913400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle112">难得我们给予他们<br />安全又肥沃的土地</p>
<p begin="3913300000t" end="3947500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle113">希望他们培养出<br />能抵御不同种族侵略的勇者</p>
<p begin="3947500000t" end="3981700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle114">一直以教国的身份为他们尽心尽力</p>
<p begin="3981700000t" end="4035900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle115">没想到他们内部<br />竟然会因为和平和富足而腐败</p>
<p begin="4035800000t" end="4077500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle116">甚至还制作毒品<br />让帝国也逐渐沦陷</p>
<p begin="4077500000t" end="4109600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle117">真是一群无药可救的废物</p>
<p begin="4109600000t" end="4136300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle118">只能改变计划了</p>
<p begin="4136300000t" end="4166300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle119">让帝国并吞王国</p>
<p begin="4166300000t" end="4196300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle120">那也许是最好的办法</p>
<p begin="4196300000t" end="4215500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle121">回到正题</p>
<p begin="4215400000t" end="4247500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle122">把送到王国的阳光圣典摧毁的人</p>
<p begin="4247500000t" end="4271300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle123">应该是魔导王没错</p>
<p begin="4271300000t" end="4304200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle124">那漆黑圣典遇到的吸血鬼</p>
<p begin="4304200000t" end="4328400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle125">鲜血的战争少女是他的伙伴吗</p>
<p begin="4328300000t" end="4350400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle126">毕竟他们都是不死者</p>
<p begin="4350400000t" end="4369200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle127">说到强者的话</p>
<p begin="4369200000t" end="4411700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle128">还有在相近的时期<br />于王国里作乱的恶魔亚达巴沃</p>
<p begin="4411700000t" end="4449600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle129">魔导王 鲜血的战争少女<br />亚达巴沃</p>
<p begin="4449600000t" end="4503800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle130">为什么会有这么多非人类的强者<br />同时出现在王国里</p>
<p begin="4503800000t" end="4528000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle131">肯定不是没有关联</p>
<p begin="4527900000t" end="4560000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle132">他们不都是那一边的人吗</p>
<p begin="4560000000t" end="4586300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle133">那冒险者莫莫又如何呢</p>
<p begin="4586300000t" end="4606300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle134">他是从哪里出现的</p>
<p begin="4606300000t" end="4647100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle135">虽然他看似消灭了吸血鬼<br />还和亚达巴沃是死对头</p>
<p begin="4647100000t" end="4674600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle136">还不是变成魔导王的伙伴吗</p>
<p begin="4674600000t" end="4725000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle137">你的意思是吸血鬼和亚达巴沃<br />魔导王和莫莫联手吗</p>
<p begin="4725000000t" end="4772500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle138">最糟的情况莫过于这四个人联手</p>
<p begin="4772500000t" end="4796300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle139">这个可能性应该很低</p>
<p begin="4796300000t" end="4828000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle140">因为是莫莫消灭吸血鬼的</p>
<p begin="4827900000t" end="4889200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle141">我们应该先思考该怎么<br />让魔导王与莫莫反目成仇吧</p>
<p begin="4889200000t" end="4930900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle142">但我们现在最好避免直接行动</p>
<p begin="4930800000t" end="4954100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle143">说得也是</p>
<p begin="4954200000t" end="4989200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle144">我们现在遭受很大的损失</p>
<p begin="4989200000t" end="5024600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle145">因为疾风走破背叛<br />害我们失去头冠和巫女公主</p>
<p begin="5024600000t" end="5054600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle146">阳光圣典被魔导王摧毁</p>
<p begin="5054600000t" end="5090000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle147">虽然复活了但漆黑圣典却出现空缺</p>
<p begin="5090000000t" end="5110400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle148">还失去了凯瑞</p>
<p begin="5110400000t" end="5167100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle149">在这种情况之下采取行动<br />根本就是自取灭亡</p>
<p begin="5167100000t" end="5190900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle150">我们应该先想办法和帝国接触</p>
<p begin="5190800000t" end="5211200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle151">打听一下情报</p>
<p begin="5211300000t" end="5263800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle152">但愿那个皇帝<br />不会对魔导王唯命是从</p>
<p begin="5288800000t" end="5308400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle153">臭家伙 混蛋 去死吧</p>
<p begin="5308300000t" end="5328700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle154">(第3集 巴哈斯帝国)<br />给我腐朽而死吧</p>
<p begin="5343800000t" end="5368800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle155">不对 他是不死者</p>
<p begin="5368800000t" end="5393800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle156">应该叫他活下去才对吗</p>
<p begin="5402100000t" end="5458400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle157">我听说过神官可以用神圣力量<br />摧毁不死者</p>
<p begin="5480000000t" end="5501700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle158">全都是那家伙…</p>
<p begin="5501700000t" end="5527500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle159">魔导王的错</p>
<p begin="5576300000t" end="5590900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle160">进来</p>
<p begin="5612100000t" end="5643400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle161">陛下 那些堆积如山的文件…</p>
<p begin="5643300000t" end="5666700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle162">是骑士们呈上来的吗</p>
<p begin="5666700000t" end="5721700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle163">对 帝国的精锐们<br />想连署一起离开骑士团</p>
<p begin="5721700000t" end="5749600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle164">他们因为卡兹平原之战丧失勇气</p>
<p begin="5749600000t" end="5778800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle165">一直害怕得睡不着觉</p>
<p begin="5778800000t" end="5823800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle166">今后还是交给我们秘书官来应对吧</p>
<p begin="5838800000t" end="5850100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle167">不用</p>
<p begin="5850000000t" end="5883300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle168">准许骑士直接提出意见的人是我</p>
<p begin="5883300000t" end="5917900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle169">而且我现在不能失去他们的支持</p>
<p begin="5917900000t" end="5937900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle170">话说回来 你有什么事</p>
<p begin="5937900000t" end="5976200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle171">是 我们收到那一国的商人联络</p>
<p begin="5976300000t" end="5994200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle172">那一国吗</p>
<p begin="5994200000t" end="6018000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle173">听说他们拥有非常棒的商品</p>
<p begin="6017900000t" end="6053300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle174">希望近期可以觐见陛下一面</p>
<p begin="6053300000t" end="6077100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle175">非常棒的商品…</p>
<p begin="6077100000t" end="6120000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle176">也就是说斯连教国也在防备魔导国</p>
<p begin="6120000000t" end="6148800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle177">所以打算协助我们吗</p>
<p begin="6148800000t" end="6204600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle178">想对抗安兹．乌尔．恭<br />就只有与教国结盟一途</p>
<p begin="6204600000t" end="6237100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle179">但请使者来这座城堡太危险了</p>
<p begin="6237100000t" end="6274200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle180">绝对不能让人知道这项计划</p>
<p begin="6300400000t" end="6314200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle181">那么陛下</p>
<p begin="6314200000t" end="6355000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle182">在竞技场前面和银丝鸟的成员会合<br />这样没问题吧</p>
<p begin="6355000000t" end="6366300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle183">好</p>
<p begin="6366300000t" end="6394200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle184">我和那一国的商人开会的期间</p>
<p begin="6394200000t" end="6415000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle185">请他们在外面看守</p>
<p begin="6415000000t" end="6435000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle186">绝对不能让别人用物理手段<br />或魔法手段</p>
<p begin="6435000000t" end="6463800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle187">偷听我们的对话内容</p>
<p begin="6463800000t" end="6508400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle188">精钢级冒险者<br />的确是人类最强的战力</p>
<p begin="6508300000t" end="6542100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle189">但终究还是属于人类的范畴</p>
<p begin="6542100000t" end="6561700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle190">我听说王国的冒险者莫莫</p>
<p begin="6561700000t" end="6592100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle191">从那个魔导王的手中保护了人民哦</p>
<p begin="6592100000t" end="6623800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle192">银丝鸟也一样是精钢级的</p>
<p begin="6623800000t" end="6648000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle193">如果无法保护我 我会伤脑筋的</p>
<p begin="6647900000t" end="6679200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle194">陛下 请您不要露出那种表情</p>
<p begin="6679200000t" end="6705900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle195">就是说啊 请您再堂堂正正一点</p>
<p begin="6705800000t" end="6738300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle196">露出像平常那样自信满满的表情吧</p>
<p begin="6738300000t" end="6777100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle197">抱歉 因为现在这里只有你们</p>
<p begin="6777100000t" end="6802100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle198">我可以稍微抱怨一下吗</p>
<p begin="6818300000t" end="6843700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle199">你们说 到底该怎么办才好</p>
<p begin="6843800000t" end="6869600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle200">为什么会出现那种怪物啊</p>
<p begin="6869600000t" end="6886700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle201">骑士们都害怕得要命</p>
<p begin="6886700000t" end="6926700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle202">就连帝国最强的王牌夫路达<br />也跑去追随他了</p>
<p begin="6926700000t" end="6956700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle203">的确 是我要求让他使用魔法的</p>
<p begin="6956700000t" end="6984600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle204">但是不调查一下他有什么能力</p>
<p begin="6984600000t" end="7008800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle205">根本想不出任何对策</p>
<p begin="7008800000t" end="7026300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle206">难道这是我的错吗</p>
<p begin="7026300000t" end="7050900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle207">所有坏事都是我的责任吗</p>
<p begin="7050800000t" end="7072500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle208">每个人都怪我</p>
<p begin="7154200000t" end="7181700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle209">可是我还不打算放弃</p>
<p begin="7181700000t" end="7207500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle210">一定有什么对策才对</p>
<p begin="7207500000t" end="7218800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle211">陛下</p>
<p begin="7218800000t" end="7260500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle212">我在上一场战争跟在魔导王身边</p>
<p begin="7260400000t" end="7295400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle213">那不是人类能赢过的存在</p>
<p begin="7295400000t" end="7341700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle214">与魔导国兵戎相见<br />简直就是愚蠢的行为吧</p>
<p begin="7341700000t" end="7378400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle215">没错 你说的话是对的</p>
<p begin="7378300000t" end="7397100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle216">但是你想想看</p>
<p begin="7397100000t" end="7428800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle217">假设魔导王消灭帝国的那一刻来临</p>
<p begin="7428800000t" end="7459600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle218">他会不会接受我们投降还是未知数</p>
<p begin="7459600000t" end="7473800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle219">这个嘛…</p>
<p begin="7473800000t" end="7494200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle220">正因为如此</p>
<p begin="7494200000t" end="7521700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle221">正因为如此才需要斯连教国</p>
<p begin="7521700000t" end="7550500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle222">那个比我国历史更悠久的国家</p>
<p begin="7550400000t" end="7590800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle223">如果拥有能对抗<br />那些家伙的武器和知识</p>
<p begin="7590800000t" end="7615400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle224">我就还能再战</p>
<p begin="7680400000t" end="7706700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle225">很荣幸初次见到您</p>
<p begin="7706700000t" end="7752100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle226">我们是接受这次护卫委托的<br />精钢级冒险者团队</p>
<p begin="7752100000t" end="7766300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle227">银丝鸟</p>
<p begin="7766300000t" end="7817600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle228">各位是我国最强的冒险者团队<br />我已经久仰大名了</p>
<p begin="7817500000t" end="7834600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle229">谢谢您 陛下</p>
<p begin="7834600000t" end="7856300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle230">我是团队的队长</p>
<p begin="7856300000t" end="7878000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle231">吟游诗人弗赖瓦尔兹</p>
<p begin="7877900000t" end="7902500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle232">那就由我介绍一下大家…</p>
<p begin="7902500000t" end="7925400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle233">拜托你别唱歌哦 队长</p>
<p begin="7925400000t" end="7947900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle234">你一唱歌我就会起鸡皮疙瘩</p>
<p begin="7957500000t" end="7976700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle235">失礼了 陛下</p>
<p begin="7976700000t" end="8001700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle236">他是我们团队的耳朵和眼睛</p>
<p begin="8001700000t" end="8021300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle237">苏德</p>
<p begin="8021300000t" end="8043800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle238">范．龙古</p>
<p begin="8043800000t" end="8065100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle239">他是我们的战士</p>
<p begin="8065000000t" end="8099200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle240">然后接着是替我们疗伤的…</p>
<p begin="8110800000t" end="8135400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle241">贫僧叫运庆</p>
<p begin="8135400000t" end="8146200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle242">原来如此</p>
<p begin="8146300000t" end="8169600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle243">那么最后这一位就是波彭咯</p>
<p begin="8169600000t" end="8187500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle244">您说得没错</p>
<p begin="8187500000t" end="8211300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle245">我们会负责保护陛下</p>
<p begin="8211300000t" end="8235500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle246">请您放心交给我们吧</p>
<p begin="8235400000t" end="8256700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle247">今天就麻烦你们了</p>
<p begin="8309600000t" end="8321700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle248">陛下</p>
<p begin="8321700000t" end="8348800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle249">这里并没有被人设下魔法道具</p>
<p begin="8348800000t" end="8379200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle250">也没有被施了魔法的迹象</p>
<p begin="8379200000t" end="8418400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle251">如果还是有人想偷听的话<br />你们有什么对策</p>
<p begin="8418300000t" end="8449200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle252">老实说都做到这种程度了<br />应该不会有问题吧</p>
<p begin="8449200000t" end="8465500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle253">我是这么想的</p>
<p begin="8465400000t" end="8482100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle254">这样啊</p>
<p begin="8482100000t" end="8493400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle255">辛苦了</p>
<p begin="8493300000t" end="8523300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle256">接下来我有非常重要的会议</p>
<p begin="8523300000t" end="8552100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle257">请你们到房间外面去看守</p>
<p begin="8552100000t" end="8599600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle258">这样我们要保护陛下会非常困难</p>
<p begin="8599600000t" end="8615900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle259">我能理解你的担忧</p>
<p begin="8615800000t" end="8653700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle260">但作为帝国的皇帝<br />这一点我不能妥协</p>
<p begin="8653800000t" end="8668800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle261">没办法了</p>
<p begin="8668800000t" end="8697100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle262">那我们就到房间外去守候了</p>
<p begin="8697100000t" end="8726300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle263">您可以告诉我们是谁要来吗</p>
<p begin="8726300000t" end="8755500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle264">听说是火之神殿<br />和风之神殿的神官长</p>
<p begin="8755400000t" end="8782900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle265">还有四位同行者</p>
<p begin="8782900000t" end="8793700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle266">我懂了</p>
<p begin="8793800000t" end="8806700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle267">那么为了安全起见</p>
<p begin="8806700000t" end="8830500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle268">破坏门锁也没关系吧</p>
<p begin="8830400000t" end="8870800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle269">如果你们认为有破坏的必要<br />那就破坏吧</p>
<p begin="8922900000t" end="8943700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle270">不可以破坏门哦</p>
<p begin="8943800000t" end="8955100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle271">为什么</p>
<p begin="8955000000t" end="8999600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle272">“本来只是想破坏门锁<br />却不小心破坏了门真是抱歉”</p>
<p begin="8999600000t" end="9023000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle273">“不过机会难得<br />就让我们也一起参加吧”</p>
<p begin="9022900000t" end="9044200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle274">作战计划不是这样吗</p>
<p begin="9044200000t" end="9065900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle275">这次就算了</p>
<p begin="9065800000t" end="9101200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle276">因为我不想和政治有关的阴谋<br />扯上关系</p>
<p begin="9101300000t" end="9115100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle277">明白了</p>
<p begin="9137500000t" end="9182100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle278">要我把你彻底拉进这个阴谋里吧</p>
<p begin="9227100000t" end="9261300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle279">不愧是精钢级…应该这么说吗</p>
<p begin="9293300000t" end="9315400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle280">因为夫路达背叛我</p>
<p begin="9315400000t" end="9353700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle281">害我失去能仰赖知识和技术的对象</p>
<p begin="9353800000t" end="9395900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle282">今后也许必须依靠<br />银丝鸟这种冒险者的力量</p>
<p begin="9421300000t" end="9439200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle283">气氛真热烈呢</p>
<p begin="9449200000t" end="9489200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle284">听说那位武王今天会久违地上场哦</p>
<p begin="9507100000t" end="9526300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle285">真是和平的景象</p>
<p begin="9526300000t" end="9542600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle286">是这样吗</p>
<p begin="9542500000t" end="9570800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle287">他们不知道帝国的状况</p>
<p begin="9570800000t" end="9614600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle288">不知道有一只怪物就近在咫尺</p>
<p begin="9633800000t" end="9648800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle289">怎么了</p>
<p begin="9648800000t" end="9675100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle290">神官长大人他们来了</p>
<p begin="9756300000t" end="9775100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle291">(帝国 火之神殿神官长)</p>
<p begin="9775000000t" end="9791700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle292">(帝国 风之神殿神官长)</p>
<p begin="9791700000t" end="9829600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle293">谢谢您邀请我们过来</p>
<p begin="9842900000t" end="9857100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle294">欢迎你们来</p>
<p begin="9857100000t" end="9871700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle295">来 请坐</p>
<p begin="9871700000t" end="9896700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle296">最高潮的比赛现在正要开始</p>
<p begin="9975800000t" end="10003700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle297">教国提出的疑问状啊</p>
<p begin="10019200000t" end="10045000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle298">像这样直接传递纸张</p>
<p begin="10045000000t" end="10071300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle299">是因为很谨慎呢</p>
<p begin="10071300000t" end="10100500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle300">还是因为不信任帝国呢</p>
<p begin="10114600000t" end="10133000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle301">这场最重要的盛大比赛</p>
<p begin="10132900000t" end="10160000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle302">艾尔．尼克斯皇帝陛下也前来观战</p>
<p begin="10160000000t" end="10186300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle303">各位 请看一下贵宾室</p>
<p begin="10205800000t" end="10225000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle304">我离席一下</p>
<p begin="10271300000t" end="10295100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle305">皇帝陛下 谢谢您</p>
<p begin="10295000000t" end="10308290000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle306">那么各位观众</p>
<p begin="10308290000t" end="10348290000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle307">接下来武王即将久违地上场决斗</p>
<p begin="10348290000t" end="10367900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle308">武王吗</p>
<p begin="10367900000t" end="10380790000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle309">武之王</p>
<p begin="10380790000t" end="10411600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle310">是赋予最强剑斗士的称号</p>
<p begin="10411700000t" end="10425890000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle311">现在这位是第八代</p>
<p begin="10425790000t" end="10445790000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle312">号称是历代最强</p>
<p begin="10445790000t" end="10476190000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle313">最近这阵子一直没有出现<br />能和他决斗的挑战者</p>
<p begin="10476300000t" end="10500900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle314">那么今天和他决斗的是…</p>
<p begin="10500800000t" end="10532100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle315">这次的决斗好像是临时决定的</p>
<p begin="10532100000t" end="10549600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle316">就连我也不知道</p>
<p begin="10549600000t" end="10583800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle317">为了制造话题性<br />他们似乎把这件事当成机密</p>
<p begin="10583800000t" end="10623800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle318">武王虽然是战斗食人妖<br />却是帝国最强的存在</p>
<p begin="10623800000t" end="10669200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle319">既然这样能不能延揽他<br />让他替帝国效力呢</p>
<p begin="10669200000t" end="10708000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle320">没想到你们这些认为只有人类<br />才是被神选上的种族的人</p>
<p begin="10707900000t" end="10728300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle321">居然会说这种话</p>
<p begin="10728300000t" end="10755400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle322">请当成是我个人的意见吧</p>
<p begin="10755400000t" end="10783700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle323">那么闲聊就到此为止 陛下</p>
<p begin="10783800000t" end="10809600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle324">可以请您回答问题吗</p>
<p begin="10809600000t" end="10820900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle325">好 我这就写</p>
<p begin="10820800000t" end="10847100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle326">不好意思让各位久等了</p>
<p begin="10847100000t" end="10880400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle327">现在欢迎挑战者进场</p>
<p begin="10888800000t" end="10922100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle328">挑战者的名字应该没有人不知道</p>
<p begin="10922100000t" end="10940400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle329">他是魔导国国王</p>
<p begin="10940400000t" end="10966200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle330">安兹．乌尔．恭陛下</p>
<p begin="11017500000t" end="11033300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle331">什么</p>
<p begin="11060400000t" end="11084200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle332">安兹．乌尔．恭</p>
<p begin="11084200000t" end="11112500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle333">不…不可能</p>
<p begin="11112500000t" end="11136700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle334">这怎么可能</p>
<p begin="11162500000t" end="11180000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle335">等一下 这是陷阱</p>
<p begin="11180000000t" end="11202500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle336">魔导国的吗 还是说…</p>
<p begin="11202500000t" end="11210400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle337">不是的</p>
<p begin="11210400000t" end="11234600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle338">地点是陛下您指定的吧</p>
<p begin="11234600000t" end="11255900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle339">是这样没错 但是…</p>
<p begin="11255800000t" end="11285400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle340">如果是我做的<br />我就不需要这么惊慌了吧</p>
<p begin="11285400000t" end="11311700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle341">您是要我们相信这点吗</p>
<p begin="11311700000t" end="11334600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle342">您是为了把我们扯进来吗</p>
<p begin="11334600000t" end="11360900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle343">还是想出卖我们呢</p>
<p begin="11360800000t" end="11390400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle344">不是 这是天大的误会</p>
<p begin="11390400000t" end="11409200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle345">情报是从哪里泄漏出去的</p>
<p begin="11409200000t" end="11418400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle346">不对</p>
<p begin="11418300000t" end="11450800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle347">难道说他完全看穿我们的行动了</p>
<p begin="11450800000t" end="11488300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle348">撒下诱饵 然后等待我们上钩吗</p>
<p begin="11488300000t" end="11501200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle349">糟了 不能离开这里…</p>
<p begin="11501300000t" end="11541700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle350">吉克尼夫．伦．法洛德<br />艾尔．尼克斯陛下</p>
<p begin="11577900000t" end="11598700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle351">好久不见了</p>
<p begin="11606300000t" end="11630500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle352">彼此彼此 恭陛下</p>
<p begin="11630400000t" end="11661700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle353">没想到竟然会在这种地方见面</p>
<p begin="11661700000t" end="11688000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle354">我也这么想</p>
<p begin="11687900000t" end="11720000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle355">如果是偶然那就可怕了</p>
<p begin="11728800000t" end="11766700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle356">不会有错 全都是他的阴谋</p>
<p begin="11766700000t" end="11785500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle357">来我和教国密谈的地方闹场</p>
<p begin="11785400000t" end="11824600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle358">阻止我们结盟 然后对两国施压</p>
<p begin="11824600000t" end="11862100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle359">那边的几位是陛下的熟人吗</p>
<p begin="11862100000t" end="11879600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle360">真是太恶毒了</p>
<p begin="11879600000t" end="11895900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle361">这是要我表明立场</p>
<p begin="11895800000t" end="11910400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle362">看我是要包庇教国</p>
<p begin="11910400000t" end="11933300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle363">还是作为魔导王的同伴出卖他们</p>
<p begin="11933300000t" end="11943700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle364">失礼了</p>
<p begin="11943800000t" end="11969600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle365">本来应该由我们自己报上姓名</p>
<p begin="11969600000t" end="12009600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle366">但我们有非常紧急的事要处理<br />必须马上离开这里</p>
<p begin="12009600000t" end="12045000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle367">我们的事就请您晚点问陛下吧</p>
<p begin="12056300000t" end="12088800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle368">这样啊 那真是太遗憾了</p>
<p begin="12088800000t" end="12116300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle369">有缘再见吧</p>
<p begin="12116300000t" end="12141700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle370">在那之前请多保重</p>
<p begin="12150400000t" end="12169200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle371">你怎么了 艾尔．尼克斯…</p>
<p begin="12169200000t" end="12193800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle372">不对 吉克尼夫陛下</p>
<p begin="12193800000t" end="12228000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle373">你的脸色不太好 是身体不适吗</p>
<p begin="12237100000t" end="12257500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle374">没…没有 我没事</p>
<p begin="12257500000t" end="12277900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle375">是吗 身体就是资本</p>
<p begin="12277900000t" end="12294600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle376">请好好保重</p>
<p begin="12294600000t" end="12329200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle377">我还有比赛要比 先告辞了</p>
<p begin="12329200000t" end="12350900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle378">你陷害了我们吧</p>
<p begin="12350800000t" end="12360000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle379">不是</p>
<p begin="12360000000t" end="12377500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle380">哪里不是了</p>
<p begin="12377500000t" end="12397100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle381">你跟他说了多少</p>
<p begin="12397100000t" end="12427500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle382">为了保护自己的国家<br />你出卖我们到什么程度</p>
<p begin="12427500000t" end="12440400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle383">请你们相信我</p>
<p begin="12440400000t" end="12470000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle384">我绝对没有泄露情报给他</p>
<p begin="12470000000t" end="12494600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle385">很遗憾 皇帝陛下</p>
<p begin="12494600000t" end="12507500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle386">等一下</p>
<p begin="12507500000t" end="12535000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle387">请告诉我神殿势力的想法</p>
<p begin="12535000000t" end="12566300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle388">你们对魔导王是怎么想的</p>
<p begin="12566300000t" end="12589600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle389">魔导王是邪恶的不死者</p>
<p begin="12589600000t" end="12622900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle390">我们绝对不会承认他是国王</p>
<p begin="12622900000t" end="12654600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle391">为此我们会寻找消灭他的手段</p>
<p begin="12654600000t" end="12684600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle392">你想出卖我们就出卖吧 皇帝</p>
<p begin="12684600000t" end="12714200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle393">被强大的恶魔魅惑的人</p>
<p begin="12722900000t" end="12745800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle394">他的智谋比我还高</p>
<p begin="12745800000t" end="12782500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle395">事情会变成这样<br />肯定全都是他的计划</p>
<p begin="12782500000t" end="12832500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle396">换作我是你们<br />应该也会觉得很难相信</p>
<p begin="12832500000t" end="12862900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle397">而且魔导王的统治非常仁慈</p>
<p begin="12862900000t" end="12887500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle398">耶．兰提尔的人民都过得很和平</p>
<p begin="12887500000t" end="12923300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle399">我们根本不知道<br />这种情况能持续多久吧</p>
<p begin="12923300000t" end="12936200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle400">你说得有道理</p>
<p begin="12936300000t" end="12951700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle401">但是…正因为如此</p>
<p begin="12951700000t" end="12975000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle402">我希望你们别采取轻率的行动</p>
<p begin="12975000000t" end="12987900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle403">然后最后</p>
<p begin="12987900000t" end="13022100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle404">请你们躲在某处<br />观看他在竞技场上战斗的模样</p>
<p begin="13022100000t" end="13051300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle405">如果有能击败他的手段 请告诉我</p>
<p begin="13065000000t" end="13091300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle406">有缘再见吧</p>
<p begin="13103800000t" end="13137100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle407">各位 让大家久等了</p>
<p begin="13137100000t" end="13157500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle408">帝国最强的斗士</p>
<p begin="13157500000t" end="13185400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle409">欢迎诞生于竞技场的伟大英雄</p>
<p begin="13185400000t" end="13211700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle410">武王进场</p>
<p begin="13211700000t" end="13251700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle411">凭我是没办法用智谋战胜他的</p>
<p begin="13251700000t" end="13288800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle412">唯一能依靠的…就只有人心了</p>
<p begin="13322900000t" end="13337100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle413">武王…</p>
<p begin="13337100000t" end="13359200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle414">加油</p>
</div>
